<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-4655] groovy.transform.EqualsAndHashCode annotation does not handle cycles</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-4655</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The groovy.transform.EqualsAndHashCode AST transformation does not handle object graphs with cycles. See the attached junit tests.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Some of the test methods I included actually pass - I just included them for completeness.  Basically, the equals method handles cycles just fine.  The hashcode method does not so all the tests related to the hashcode method fail.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is a pretty serious issue because these object structures are common with some frameworks (like orm tools)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
